findAll


java.util.Collection<PlateInspection> findAll(BusinessCriteria criteria)
                                              throws BusinessException



    
Finds all inspections. This will only be used by an administrator.
    Not sure that this will get used much as it will probably crash everything!
    

    

    

    

    

    

    

    

        
Parameters:

        
person - - find all the inspections for this
        person. if it is null, find all inspections for all.

        
userOnly - - only find inspections for this user
        (true) or this user and all the groups to which they belong (false)

        
paging -

        
Returns:

        
A list of all plate inspections for all time.

        
Throws:

        
BusinessException
